Class CarFerry

  • java.lang.Object
    • CarFerry
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ILoadable, IMovable

    public class CarFerry
extends java.lang.Object
implements IMovable, ILoadable
    Class for a ferry which can transport a number of cars. First car in is also first car out.
